msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This module is designed to help users who have difficulty hearing audible "
"cues, or who have difficulty using a keyboard."
msgstr ""
"See moodul on mõeldud abiks inimestele, kellel on raskusi kuulmisega või "
"klaviatuuri kasutamisega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The module is divided into five tabs: <link linkend=\"access-bell"
#| "\"><guilabel>Bell</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-modifier-keys"
#| "\"><guilabel>Modifier keys</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-"
#| "keyboard-filters\"><guilabel>Keyboard Filters</guilabel></link>, <link "
#| "linkend=\"access-activation-gestures\"><guilabel>Activation Gestures</"
#| "guilabel></link> and <guilabel>Screen Reader</guilabel>."
msgid ""
"The module is divided into six tabs: <link linkend=\"access-bell"
"\"><guilabel>Bell</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-modifier-keys"
"\"><guilabel>Modifier keys</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-"
"keyboard-filters\"><guilabel>Keyboard Filters</guilabel></link>, <link "
"linkend=\"access-activation-gestures\"><guilabel>Activation Gestures</"
"guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"mouse-navigation\"><guilabel>Mouse "
"Navigation</guilabel></link>, and <link linkend=\"access-screenreader"
"\"><guilabel>Screen Reader</guilabel></link>."
msgstr ""
"Moodul on jagatud viieks kaardiks: <link linkend=\"access-bell"
"\"><guilabel>Signaal</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-modifier-keys"
"\"><guilabel>Muuteklahvid</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-keyboard-"
"filters\"><guilabel>Klaviatuuri filtrid</guilabel></link>, <link linkend="
"\"access-activation-gestures\"><guilabel>Aktiveerimistoimingud</guilabel></"
"link> ja <guilabel>Ekraanilugeja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bell"
msgstr "Signaal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This panel is divided into an <guilabel>Audible Bell</guilabel> section and "
"a <guilabel>Visible Bell</guilabel> section."
msgstr ""
"See paneel on omakorda jagatud kaheks: <guilabel>Helisignaal</guilabel> ja "
"<guilabel>Visuaalne signaal</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top check box labeled <guilabel>Use System Bell</guilabel>, determines "
"whether the normal System bell rings. If this option is disabled, the System "
"bell will be silenced."
msgstr ""
"Ülal paiknev märkekast <guilabel>Süsteemse helisignaali kasutamine</"
"guilabel> määrab, kas süsteem kasutab helisignaali või mitte. Kui kast ei "
"ole märgitud, süsteemset helisignaali ei kasutata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next check box down can be used to play a different sound whenever the "
"system bell is triggered. To activate, place a mark in the check box labeled "
"<guilabel>Use customized bell</guilabel>, and enter the complete pathname to "
"the sound file in the text box labeled <guilabel>Sound to play</guilabel>. "
"If you want, you can select the <guibutton>Browse</guibutton> button to "
"navigate through your filesystem to find the exact file."
msgstr ""
"Järgmises märkekastis saab määrata tavalisest erineva heli esitamise "
"süsteemse helisignaali kõlamisel. Aktiveerimiseks märgi esmalt ära kast "
"<guilabel>Kohandatud helisignaal</guilabel> ja kirjuta siis helifaili "
"täielik asukoht kasti <guilabel>Mängitav helifail</guilabel>. Soovi korral "
"võid klõpsata nupule <guibutton>Lehitse...</guibutton>, et otsida ilmuva "
"failidialoogi abil sobiv fail."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For those users who have difficulty hearing the System bell, or those "
#| "users who have a silent computer, &kde; offers the <emphasis>visible "
#| "bell</emphasis>. This provides a visual signal (inverting the screen or "
#| "flashing a color across it) when the system bell would normally sound."
msgid ""
"For those users who have difficulty hearing the System bell, or those users "
"who have a silent computer, &kde; offers the <emphasis>visual bell</"
"emphasis>. This provides a visual signal (inverting the screen or flashing a "
"color across it) when the system bell would normally sound."
msgstr ""
"Kasutajatele, kellel on raskusi süsteemse helisignaali kuulmisel või kel on "
"helita arvuti, pakub &kde; <emphasis>visuaalset helisignaali</emphasis>. See "
"näitab ajal, mil muidu peaks kõlama süsteemne helisignaal, teatud nähtavat "
"signaali (näiteks pannes ekraani vilkuma)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To use the visible bell, first place a mark in the check box labeled "
#| "<guilabel>Use visible bell</guilabel>."
msgid ""
"To use the visual bell, first place a mark in the check box labeled "
"<guilabel>Use visual bell</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Visuaalse helisignaali kasutamiseks märgi esmalt kastike <guilabel>Visuaalse "
"signaali kasutamine</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can then select between <guilabel>Invert screen</guilabel>, or "
"<guilabel>Flash screen</guilabel>. If you select <guilabel>Invert screen</"
"guilabel>, all colors on the screen will be reversed. If you choose "
"<guilabel>Flash screen</guilabel>, you can choose the color by clicking the "
"button to the right of the <guilabel>Flash screen</guilabel> selection."
msgstr ""
"Valida saab võimaluste <guilabel>Ekraani inverteerimine</guilabel> ja "
"<guilabel>Ekraani vilgutamine</guilabel> vahel. <guilabel>Ekraani "
"inverteerimine</guilabel> tähendab kõigi ekraanivärvide muutmist "
"vastupidiseks. <guilabel>Ekraani vilgutamise</guilabel> valimise korral saab "
"värvi valida paremal pool asuvast värvivaliku nupust."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The spin box can be used to adjust the duration of the visible bell. The "
"default value is 500 msec, or half a second."
msgstr ""
"Kerimiskastis saab kohandada visuaalse signaali kestust. Vaikimisi on see "
"500 ms ehk pool sekundit."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier keys"
msgstr "Muuteklahvid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are the two sections <guilabel>Sticky Keys</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Locking Keys</guilabel> to this panel."
msgstr ""
"See paneel on jagatud kaheks: <guilabel>Kleepuvad klahvid</guilabel> ja "
"<guilabel>Lukustavad klahvid</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use Sticky Keys"
msgstr "Kleepuvate klahvide kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is enabled, you can press and release the &Shift;, &Alt; "
#| "or &Ctrl; keys, and then press another key to get a key combo (example: "
#| "<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Alt; <keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo> "
#| "could be done with &Ctrl; then &Alt; then <keycap>Del</keycap>)."
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, you can press and release the &Shift;, &Alt; or "
"&Ctrl; keys, and then press another key to get a key combo (example: "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Del;</keycombo> could be done with "
"&Ctrl;, then &Alt; and then &Del;)."
msgstr ""
"Kui see on lubatud, saab kasutaja &Shift;, &Alt; või &Ctrl; klahvi vajutades "
"ning lahti lastes ja seejärel mõnda muud klahvi vajutades kasutada "
"klahvikombinatsioone (näide: kombinatsiooni <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; &Alt; <keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo> võib korraga vajutamise "
"asemel ka sooritada ükshaaval &Ctrl;, &Alt; ja <keycap>Del</keycap> klahve "
"vajutades)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also in this section is a check box labeled <guilabel>Lock Sticky Keys</"
"guilabel>. If this check box is enabled, the &Alt;, &Ctrl; and &Shift; keys "
"stay <quote>selected</quote> until you <quote>de-selected</quote> them."
msgstr ""
"Selles sektsioonis asub ka märkekast <guilabel>Kleepuvate klahvide "
"lukustamine</guilabel>. Kui see on lubatud, jäävad &Alt;, &Ctrl; ja &Shift; "
"<quote>sisse</quote>, kuni kasutaja neid spetsiaalselt <quote>lahti</quote> "
"ei lase."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "As an example:"
msgstr "Näide:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "With <guilabel>Lock Sticky Keys</guilabel> disabled:"
msgstr "Kui <guilabel>kleepuvate klahvide lukustamine</guilabel> on keelatud:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you press the &Shift; key then press the <keycap>F</keycap> key, the "
"computer interprets this as <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F</"
"keycap></keycombo>. Now if you type a <keycap>P</keycap>, the computer "
"interprets this as the letter p (no shift)."
msgstr ""
"Kasutaja vajutab klahvi &Shift; ning seejärel <keycap>F</keycap>. Arvuti "
"tõlgendab seda käsuna <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo>. Seejärel vajutab kasutaja <keycap>p</keycap> ning arvuti "
"tõlgendab seda tähena p (mitte suurtähena)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "With <guilabel>Lock Sticky Keys</guilabel> enabled:"
msgstr "Kui <guilabel>kleepuvate klahvide lukustamine</guilabel> on lubatud:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you press the &Shift; key <emphasis>twice</emphasis> then press the "
"<keycap>F</keycap> key, the computer interprets this as <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>. Now if you type a <keycap>P</"
"keycap>, the computer interprets this as the letter P (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>). To de-select the &Shift; "
"key, press it again."
msgstr ""
"Kasutaja vajutab <emphasis>kaks korda</emphasis> klahvi &Shift; ning "
"seejärel <keycap>F</keycap>. Arvuti tõlgendab seda käsuna <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>. Seejärel vajutab kasutaja "
"<keycap>p</keycap> ning arvuti tõlgendab seda tähena P (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>). Klahvi &Shift; "
"lahtilukustamiseks tuleb seda veel kord vajutada."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Filters"
msgstr "Klaviatuuri filtrid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179 index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two sections to this panel."
msgstr "Sellel paneelil on kaks sektsiooni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use slow keys"
msgstr "Aeglaste klahvide kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, you must hold the key down for a specified length "
"of time (adjustable with the spin box) before the keystroke will be "
"accepted. This helps prevent accidental key strokes."
msgstr ""
"Kui see on lubatud, peab kasutaja klahvi teatud aja all hoidma (ajaühikut "
"saab määrata kerimiskastis), enne kui arvuti selle teada võtab. See aitab "
"ära hoida juhuslikke eksimusi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use bounce keys"
msgstr "Põrkavate klahvide kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, you must wait for a specified length of time "
"(configurable with the spin box) before the next key press can be accepted. "
"This prevents accidental multiple key strokes."
msgstr ""
"Kui see on lubatud, peab kasutaja ootama teatud ajavahemiku (seda saab "
"määrata kerimiskastis), enne kui arvuti võtab teadmiseks järgmise "
"klahvivajutuse. See hoiab ära juhusliku mitme klahvi korraga vajutamise."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activation Gestures"
msgstr "Aktiveerimistoimingud"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Activation Gestures</guilabel> with these options:"
msgstr "<guilabel>Aktiveerimistoimingud</guilabel> järgmiste valikutega:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use gestures for activating sticky keys and slow keys"
msgstr "Toimingute kasutamine kleepuvate ja aeglaste klahvide aktiveerimiseks"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can activate keyboard gestures that turn on the following features:"
msgstr ""
"Siin saab aktiveerida klaviatuuritoimingud, mis lülitavad sisse järgmised "
"võimalused:"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse Keys: Press &Shift;+NumLock"
msgstr "Hiireklahvid: &Shift;+NumLock vajutamine"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sticky keys: Press &Shift; key 5 consecutive times"
msgstr "Kleepuvad klahvid: klahvi &Shift; vajutamine viis korda järjest"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slow keys: Hold down &Shift; for 8 seconds"
msgstr "Aeglased klahvid: klahvi &Shift; allhoidmine 8 sekundit"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Turn sticky keys and slow keys off after a certain period of inactivity"
msgstr ""
"Kleepuvad ja aeglased klahvid lülitatakse pärast teatud tegevusetust välja"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Notification</guilabel> with these options:"
msgstr "<guilabel>Märguanded</guilabel> järgmiste valikutega:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the system bell whenever a gesture is used to turn an accessibility "
"feature on or off"
msgstr ""
"Süsteemse heli kasutamine hõlbustusfunktsioonide sisse/väljalülitamisel"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show a confirmation dialog whenever a keyboard accessibility feature is "
"turned on or off"
msgstr ""
"Kinnituse küsimine klaviatuuri kasutamise hõlbustusfunktsioonide sisse/"
"väljalülitamisel"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, &kde; will show a confirmation dialog whenever a "
"keyboard accessibility feature is turned on or off."
msgstr ""
"Märkimise korral näitab &kde; kinnitusdialoogi alati, kui klaviatuuri "
"kasutamise hõlbustusfunktsioonid sisse või välja lülitatakse."

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ensure you know what you are doing if you uncheck it, as the keyboard "
"accessibility settings will then always be applied without confirmation."
msgstr ""
"Ole selle valiku väljalülitamisega ettevaatlik, sest sellisel juhul "
"rakendatakse kõiki klaviatuuri kasutamise hõlbustusfunktsioone alati ilma "
"kinnitust küsimata."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use &kde;'s system notification mechanism whenever a keyboard accessibility "
"feature is turned on or off"
msgstr ""
"&kde; süsteemi märguannete kasutamine klaviatuuri kasutamise "
"hõlbustusfunktsioonide sisse/väljalülitamisel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Configure Notifications</guibutton> button to open a "
"dialog which allows you to edit the notifications for status changes of all "
"keys."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Seadista märguandeid</guibutton> dialoogi "
"avamiseks, kus saab muuta kõigi klahvide olekumuutuste märguandeid."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse Navigation"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab allows you to configure the keyboard number pad keys as a mouse-"
"type device. This may be useful when you are working on a device without "
"another pointing device, or where you have no other use for the number pad."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move pointer with keyboard (using the num pad)"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable keyboard mouse mode, you need to select the check box labeled "
"<guilabel>Move pointer with keyboard (using the num pad)</guilabel>. When "
"you do this, the other settings will become enabled, and you can customize "
"the keyboard pointer behavior further, if required."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The various keys on the number pad move in the direction you would expect. "
"Note that you can move diagonally as well as up, down, left and right. The "
"<keycap>5</keycap> key emulates a click to a pointer button, typically "
"&LMB;. You change which button is emulated by using the <keycap>/</keycap> "
"key (which makes it &LMB;), <keycap>*</keycap> key (which makes it &MMB;) "
"and <keycap>-</keycap> (which makes it &RMB;). Using the <keycap>+</keycap> "
"emulates a double click to the selected pointer button. You can use the "
"<keycap>0</keycap> key to emulate holding down the selected pointer button "
"(for easy dragging), and then use the <keycap>.</keycap> to emulate "
"releasing the selected pointer button."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Acceleration delay"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the time (in milliseconds) between the initial key press and the "
"first repeated motion event for mouse key acceleration."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Repeat interval"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the time in milliseconds between repeated motion events for mouse "
"key acceleration."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Acceleration time"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the time in milliseconds before the pointer reaches a maximum speed "
"for mouse key acceleration."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maximum speed"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the maximum speed in pixels per second the pointer can reach for "
"mouse key acceleration."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pointer acceleration"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is the amount of acceleration to apply to mouse key acceleration."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screen Reader"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Install a screen reader application like <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Orca_(assistive_technology)\">Orca</ulink> together with "
"<application>speech-dispatcher</application>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Test that sound from speech dispatcher works using the command <command>spd-"
"say hello</command> in a terminal."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition you need a text to speech synthesizer like &eg; "
"<application>espeak</application>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable the screen reader in the checkbox, logout and restart your desktop "
"session."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For &plasma; itself, make sure to use the traditional <guilabel>Application "
"Menu</guilabel>, and check that this menu has a keyboard shortcut associated "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo>). When "
"pressing this shortcut, the menu should open and be read when navigating the "
"menu with the arrow keys."
msgstr ""

